images.desc: This is what the intersection looks like when facing northward.

instructions: Go to Nolte Center level B. Make your way towards the west-most point of the building.
There should be a tunnel entrance, which leads to an intersection (the first picture).
You will be coming from the rightmost path, so you will navigate around the wall to get to the center path.
There will be some stairs, and on the right an entrance to the nolte center garage.
